Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.68,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這裡真是大到感覺會迷路的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:17.25,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯 我也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:21.25,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但這別墅也太高級了吧 竟然連溫泉都有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:25.50,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是啊 竟然拿來辦合宿 感覺有點浪費啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:26.42,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:28.99,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這裡本來是我曾祖母在住的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:31.36,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是後來才改建成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:34.64,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}聽說發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:36.09,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}唯同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:40.11,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎麼了嗎? 一臉心事重重的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:41.73,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.51,0:00:44.11,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:46.85,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}現在 正值暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:28.73,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}唯同學 帽子找到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:31.51,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯 在桌子上找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:34.89,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}話說 今天是幾號來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:37.73,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}欸? 十三號啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:39.85,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}十三...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:43.90,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦!? 已經十三號了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:46.62,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯 七月十三號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:49.59,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}七...七月?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:50.88,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:53.77,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:59.44,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}花梨在暑假也會很忙吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:03.72,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯 因為有演唱會和各種活動要忙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:08.01,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}古川同學妳呢? 暑假有什麼打算嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:13.53,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}該做什麼才好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:36.18,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是不是不該去干涉這個時間軸的事象呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:42.22,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}還是該從現在就開始關注佳織同學的一舉一動呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:48.08,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我已經不曉得 這種狀況該怎麼辦才好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:54.39,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}都來到這裡了 幹嘛還擺著那副死氣沉沉的表情啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:04:00.99,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 那個...我對合宿並不是很了解...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:06.90,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}講是講合宿 但我們也只是很普通的出來玩而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:10.52,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}去海邊玩啦 放個煙火 烤個肉之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:14.16,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好像很有趣的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:18.73,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}都是些我沒體驗過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:22.50,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那就趁這次全部體驗一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.07,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:25.33,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}唯同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.76,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}既然都加入天文學會了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:33.34,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就好好地享受此時此刻的當下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.49,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}把煩惱拋到九霄雲外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:46.57,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}此時此刻的當下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:51.54,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}為什麼這次會來到時間偏移這麼多的時間軸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.65,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}現在就算想這些 也得不出什麼答案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:58.90,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}反正想也想不透
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:04.57,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那倒不如什麼都不去想 好好地享受當下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.31,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那 我就好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.26,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真是極樂世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:20.98,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}溫泉真是日本優秀的culture啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:26.23,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}打擾了 請問方便讓我一起入浴嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:30.58,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}請問怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:34.97,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好 結束~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:35.97,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真的假的!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:37.80,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這樣 又是我當富豪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:43.90,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不過話說回來 這裡好多看起來很昂貴的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:48.58,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這棟別墅 是曾祖母拿來放收藏品的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:52.61,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}雖然她在我剛出生不久就過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:54.93,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但聽說她是個相當古怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.82,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}作為華宮研究所的創立者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:02.23,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}聽說她是當時少見的女性科學家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:09.19,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}您的曾祖母大人是在華宮軍事工廠擔任技術開發的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.79,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}相當優秀的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:17.57,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}在來這裡的途中 我好像有在附近看到一間像廢棄工廠的建築物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:22.55,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是的 那就是曾經的軍事工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:27.82,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那附近人煙稀少 相當危險 請不要靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:31.84,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那裡也曾被曾祖母當作她的研究設施
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.88,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}聽說她好像在那裡做一些奇怪的實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.57,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}也聽說過有人在那裡看到幽靈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:39.62,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}要不要去試膽啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:41.90,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.11,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:44.36,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:54.79,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.92,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}今年我買了新泳衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.99,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}如何啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:05.47,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 嗯...還不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:06.93,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:07.97,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.08,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}秋山同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.06,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:16.18,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這件是從華宮同學那裡借來的 看起來會不會很奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:18.35,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}Very sexy~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:21.35,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那根手指是什麼意思啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:26.63,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}多說兩句好話嘛 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:28.98,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:32.36,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}Don't mind, don't mind~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:32.95,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我要揍人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:34.98,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}給我站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:41.35,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}請不要做危險的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.77,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:46.99,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不用這麼擔心啦 我們都不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:50.99,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那麼 我四點來接你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:53.66,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯 那就麻煩你囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:07:59.67,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小唯 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.06,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:48.16,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}唯同學不一起去玩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.19,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯 我有一點累了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:52.35,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:56.47,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}看唯同學妳開心的樣子 我也很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.69,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這就是所謂的暑假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:02.94,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:06.68,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}因為 現在會因為暑假而感動的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:10.19,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}找遍全日本 大概也只有唯同學妳而已了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:16.74,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}晚上我們準備放煙火哦 妳就好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:19.83,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}煙火 好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:22.10,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:27.52,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:31.27,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}才剛講完的說...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:39.73,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}看來還會下一陣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:44.00,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}學姊 今天就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:48.06,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}也是 那我打電話請人來接吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:02.99,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:07.11,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}打不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:12.11,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:13.98,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}　沙學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:13.98,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}{\fn DFGHSGothic-W5\pos(865,1050) }凪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:17.40,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}雨看起來是暫時不會停了 我們換個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:20.80,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}看來這麼做會比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.14,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}結果還是來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.78,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這裡就是曾經的軍事工廠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.68,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我也是第一次來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.40,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}感覺像廢墟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:48.88,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}在雨停之前 我們就來exploration吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:52.33,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}Exploration? 探險嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:53.29,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:58.22,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不要做太危險的事喔 不然會被作之進罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.09,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}有點令人興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:04.05,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}吶 你們真的要去喔?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:42.59,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}地下道?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:43.99,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}應該是倉庫之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:47.97,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}入口這麼小 應該放不了太大的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.55,0:11:49.55,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:52.23,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真想下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:53.56,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:55.38,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}要下去看看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:57.36,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:01.60,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}喂~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.22,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好像蠻深的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.63,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}電還通著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:13.57,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這裡會不會是防空洞之類的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:15.85,Sub,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:17.31,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}比起那個 感覺比較像研究設施之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:21.34,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這裡如果是屬於　沙家的東西的話 搞不好會藏有什麼寶藏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:21.34,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}{\fn DFGHSGothic-W5\pos(605,1050) }凪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:25.09,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}雨好像停了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:28.28,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}難得都來了 就再往裡面走一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.91,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳是那種在恐怖電影中最早領便當的類型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.55,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}隨便分個組 分頭去探險看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:38.20,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}二十分鐘後在入口處集合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:39.23,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:43.82,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}無視我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.50,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:57.78,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒半個人在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:58.70,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:03.74,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這也是暑假會進行的活動嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:07.45,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}呃 說是應該也算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.44,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:12.99,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是在好什麼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.76,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那麼 就進這個房間看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:17.42,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我好興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:24.08,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這裡是...寢室?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:26.78,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}應該說是保健室之類的地方吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:30.46,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這種地方感覺就會有ghost跑出來...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:31.85,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是誰!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:34.30,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:35.66,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}奏?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.35,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好痛啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:39.64,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}奏 你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:43.49,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}有受傷嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:49.17,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:51.95,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不是幽靈 真是可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:54.22,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}機會難得 就拍個照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:56.21,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:58.32,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}一片漆黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.16,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:02.90,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我是有帶手機啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:04.73,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這裡應該沒有訊號吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:07.61,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不是啦 是想說拿來當手電筒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:11.47,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}奏 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:14.37,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯 說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:19.06,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}再稍微等一下吧 搞不好等等電就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:22.61,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯...但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:26.56,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}無論如何 在眼睛習慣黑暗前都別輕舉妄動會比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:28.93,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:30.16,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}佐佐木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:31.12,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:32.06,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}麻煩過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:33.15,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:36.58,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:39.63,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我現在就過去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:42.45,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎麼了? 發生什麼事了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:52.07,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}供電好像不太穩定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:54.42,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}會不會是打雷造成的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:15:00.30,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}避免危險 在看不清楚路的情況下 還是別四處亂跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:02.42,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:03.90,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}什麼? 怎麼回事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:08.96,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這個洞是什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:11.14,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}黑漆漆的 什麼都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.85,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}感覺都是些艱澀難懂的書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:19.03,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這是德語吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:22.20,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}比起那個 妳看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:23.57,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.40,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:29.65,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦? 這個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:38.20,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}奏?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:39.62,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.34,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}奏!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:43.62,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}奏...奏啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:49.21,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎麼辦啊? 他好像失去意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.11,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}奏 奏!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:53.20,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}佐佐木同學 請冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:56.03,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是不是該把他敲醒啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:58.76,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不 現在還是別動他會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:02.75,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}比起那個 我們先和華宮同學他們匯合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:09.18,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}睡著了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:11.94,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:15.31,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這算什麼啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:20.07,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}應該是太累了吧 竟然在這種地方睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:23.09,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這該不會是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:27.71,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不過話說回來 奏在床底下做什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.25,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:51.66,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不...不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:55.78,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這是舊式的收音機吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:11.94,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦? 小佳織?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.53,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}K...Kenny
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:16.78,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:18.10,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}佳織?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.94,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}什麼嘛 原來是佳織啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.65,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:30.42,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}幽...幽靈 出...出現啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:31.27,Sub,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那 剛才那個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:34.56,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}總之 先和奏同學他們匯合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:36.50,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}說...說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:39.57,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}奏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.11,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}喂~ 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:44.88,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不行 完全沒反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:46.64,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}應該是累壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:47.94,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}Kenny
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:48.53,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:53.31,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個...那張床下面有沒有什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:55.92,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}欸? 床下?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:17:59.80,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:02.69,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:07.50,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}雖然不清楚是不是幽靈 但確實是有什麼東西在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:09.72,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}總之 先離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.43,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}撒嬌也沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:12.56,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:15.21,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小唯她...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:21.43,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:24.32,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}麻煩妳了 我在這裡等妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:25.22,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:26.89,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}佳織 走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:28.79,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}欸? 我也要去喔?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:29.97,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.18,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}唯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.52,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}古川唯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:39.26,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不過 這裡也太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:43.17,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這裡就是　沙學姊昨天說過的地方吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:43.17,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}{\fn DFGHSGothic-W5\pos(728,1050) }凪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:48.88,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}雖然說是研究設施 但這看起來根本就是下水道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:50.70,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:53.99,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我快尿出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:01.44,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我記得應該有...吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:13.46,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}去吧 佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.35,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我在這裡等妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.72,Sub,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.16,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}給妳 用這個來照明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.81,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:29.16,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我不進去 我是絕對不會進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:31.05,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.69,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}快點 不然要尿出來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:12.56,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}佳織?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:19.59,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}佳織? 佳織!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:55.95,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳終於現身啦 幽靈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:21:01.38,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就我們來看 您才是幽靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:04.98,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}華宮小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:14.68,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是嗎 原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:18.14,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}令人一時難以置信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:26.38,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯 這名為AI單元的匣子 在八十年後的未來也還是個未解之謎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:31.06,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}只知道它是個會對時間和空間造成影響的歐帕茲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:31.06,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\fs30\pos(1456,985)}OOPArt
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:32.53,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}歐帕茲?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:32.53,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\fs30\pos(944,985)}OOPArt
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:34.51,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:41.04,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就是「用對那個時代來說不可能實現的科學技術製作出來的東西」之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:46.38,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}聽不太懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:49.82,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我也是從祖母那裡拿到這個的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:52.59,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}還以為它只是個普通的玻璃盒而已的說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.07,0:21:53.92,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:56.14,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我還有很多問題想問妳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:22:02.05,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}比如說像 妳現在的穿著 在妳的時代是很平常的事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:05.72,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}其他人手上拿著的閃閃發光的東西又是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:09.01,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}還有 只有妳可以操作那個匣子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:14.84,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}對不起 因為回答這些問題可能會對歷史造成影響...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:17.93,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}講這種話 自己聽起來都覺得有點刺耳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:19.59,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.57,0:22:21.63,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那 我只問這個就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:25.61,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這場戰爭 日本最後怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.62,0:22:27.71,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這個嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:30.37,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.61,0:22:36.70,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:40.55,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}話說 連　沙學姊都在啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:40.55,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}{\fn DFGHSGothic-W5\pos(868,1050) }凪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:43.64,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}而且還比我們先找到唯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:47.61,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我可是費了好大一番功夫啊 佳織又昏過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.44,0:22:52.57,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}剛才真是對不起啊 我沒打算要嚇妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:54.67,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}欸? 剛才?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:22:56.77,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}剛才那個是　沙學姊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:22:56.77,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}{\fn DFGHSGothic-W5\pos(1008,1050) }凪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:22:57.83,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:02.88,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這樣啊 什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.58,0:23:07.13,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那麼 我們快點離開這種地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.35,0:23:09.84,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我覺得我不是很喜歡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.94,0:23:14.02,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不好意思 妳們先回去找秋山同學他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:17.78,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我們再聊幾句就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.04,0:23:24.26,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是嗎 那我們就先過去囉 先走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.92,0:23:34.15,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}華宮小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:37.20,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳們是朋友嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:41.55,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯...算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.04,0:23:50.06,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}感覺真不錯呢 等這場戰爭結束後 我來當學校的老師好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.36,0:23:57.52,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:24:01.39,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}佳織 妳差不多該醒過來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:01.94,Sub,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.52,0:24:06.09,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}學姊!? 妳什麼時候回來的?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:10.77,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}回來? 我一直都待在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.78,0:24:16.41,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}愛理同學? 妳怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.61,0:24:19.64,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我不喜歡這種過分的玩笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.80,0:24:34.69,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.85,0:24:38.06,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我好像突然睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.22,0:24:42.38,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個時候的事 我完全沒印象了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.72,0:24:46.67,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我是不覺得自己有這麼累啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.53,0:24:54.02,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.86,0:24:57.10,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}Come on! 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.25,0:24:57.94,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.15,0:24:59.21,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}欸? 等...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.70,0:25:12.16,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不過話說回來 真是嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.56,0:25:16.37,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}你們竟然從地下的酒窖裡跑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.34,0:25:18.14,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.69,0:25:20.45,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}為什麼妳會知道那個出口啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.04,0:25:23.18,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是某人告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.08,0:25:24.90,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}某人?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.23,0:25:27.39,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是的 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.44,0:25:30.32,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我就不過問了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.41,0:25:35.40,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}對了 關於這個
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.74,0:25:36.87,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.23,0:25:44.14,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真是令人懷念啊 這位就是您的曾祖母大人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.83,0:25:46.56,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}和我長得一模一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.39,0:25:50.37,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我想起了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.86,0:25:57.60,Nomal,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}現在的內濱學園 就是您的曾祖母大人所創立的學園
